      "q": "How much does Department of Veterans Affairs spend on contracts?",
      "a": "Department of Veterans Affairs has $51.1B in contract obligations for FY2026 to date. The agency recorded 54,736 awards in the period with an average award size of $933K, and obligations fell 34.8% year over year."
