    {
      "q": "What does Veterans Affairs buy?",
      "a": "Veterans Affairs buys a mix of medical and IT goods and services. Top NAICS categories for FY2026 to date are Direct Health and Medical Insurance Carriers at $14.4B, Pharmaceutical Preparation Manufacturing at $9.9B, Offices of Physicians (except Mental Health Specialists) at $7.6B, Computer Systems Design Services at $2.9B, and Software Publishers at $580M."
